<br>
Option 2:<br>
lv 54<br>
Earthen Grasp<br>
400 mana<br>
18 secs duration<br>
2 secs cast time<br>
<br>
Root NPC in place. Higher taunt than a normal root spell, higher chance of breaking with a nuke.<br>
<br>
<br>
I made the lv 34 a 300hp pet so high lv mages won't use it because of the lower mana cost (we know a 300hps pet last 2 secs against a high lv mob). <br>
<br>
Making a root spell that cost a lot of mana will prevent abuse but will still be useful for when we get jump. Making it high taunt and easy to break will make it less useful for crowd control since we know the mob will go straight for us after it breaks. <br>
<br>
